{
  "stem": "17606.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 154.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They went in the-- in the morning, came back in the evening.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And when they're following, they sometimes for a few days, sometimes only for one day.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "If they didn't they manage to get a quota, then they started to grab from the state with the help of the Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So by the way, the chief of police was a convert.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "His original name was [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Shenkman. ?] Then he became a high ranking officer in the Polish police, converted himself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And his name was [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Josef Sharinksi. ?] It was a miserable character.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You know, one convert is worse than 10 born guys.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he organized the police.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Police was about-- I would say about 1,000 of 1,500 men.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of them, very honest Jewish boys.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some used the opportunity.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't want to say they were collaborators.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they used for personal gains.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, OK, maybe they were collaborators, special the time when the final action started.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe to save their own lives, they-- they were collaborators.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the worse [INAUDIBLE] was a coward.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because he was told the final solution camp that on June 22, the day he committed suicide, the action of resettling, so-called, the Jews from Warsaw will commence.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Instead he'll tell us [INAUDIBLE], he just shot himself, a coward's way out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If he intended already to shot himself, he could say it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was a very little man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That deviated from what I was saying before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it just came to me that I left this out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After the first action, we go back a little bit before we go into the first action.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had infiltrated the Jewish military organization all positions in the police and in the people who were cleaning the gestapo headquarters.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
